caption.p: Induction of cell death by E. intisy essential oil in HL-60 and HL-60R cells. Representative example of flow cytometry analysis of cell death and cell cycle in the HL-60 and HL-60R cells treated with 25 Î¼g/mL of E. intisy essential oil for 24 h. The profiles of propidium iodide-stained DNA are shown. Numbers in the panels indicate the % of the events in the preG 0-G 1 position.
